<h1 class="headline">Helping you find restrooms <span class="subtitle">that don&rsquo;t stink beyond the possible</span></h1>

<p>Have you ever wanted to keep track of the best and worst restrooms at Case Western Reserve University? Probably not, but now you can.</p>

<%= render "buildings/near_me", buildings: nil %>

<div class="left">
  <h2>Most Popular Buildings</h2>
  <ul class="two_columns">
    <% @most_popular_buildings.each do |building| %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to building.name, building %>
      </li>
    <%end %>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="right">
  <h2>Random Buildings</h2>
  <ul class="two_columns">
    <% @random_buildings.each do |building| %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to building.name, building %>
      </li>
    <%end %>
  </ul>
</div>